00:33:22,407 --> 00:33:26,241
All l can think of is 38 kids standing
individually on lonely corners...

470
00:33:26,327 --> 00:33:28,522
waiting for a bus
that will never come.

471
00:33:28,607 --> 00:33:31,565
Put your goat leggings on
and try to blend in.

472
00:33:36,487 --> 00:33:39,524
[ Barking ]

473
00:33:43,447 --> 00:33:46,007
