475
00:33:50,007 --> 00:33:53,158
You have to admire their techniques
in crowd control.

476
00:33:53,247 --> 00:33:57,365
Yeah. Cosy little group.
Just like your local Rotarians.

477
00:33:57,447 --> 00:34:01,645
Listen, we get a little wild
at times, sure...

478
00:34:01,727 --> 00:34:03,957
but nothing like this.

479
00:34:16,647 --> 00:34:21,562
