507
00:36:19,007 --> 00:36:20,565
l do consecrate.

508
00:36:20,647 --> 00:36:24,845
With this lion's mane,
he does consecrate.

509
00:36:24,927 --> 00:36:29,205
All that's missing is one humongous,
30-foot, groundhog-gulping reptile.

510
00:36:29,287 --> 00:36:32,563
For the final touch
to our brew tonight...

511
00:36:32,647 --> 00:36:36,845
a pristine virgin
in a gown of white.

512
00:36:48,887 --> 00:36:51,242
Evil bringeth here our plea.

513
00:36:51,327 --> 00:36:54,046
She's as pure as she can be.

514
00:36:54,127 --> 00:36:56,800
White and clean as driven snow.

515
00:36:56,887 --> 00:36:59,321
From Orange County, here we go!

516
00:36:59,407 --> 00:37:01,921
[ Cheering ]

