519
00:37:12,647 --> 00:37:14,717
Virgin! Virgin!

520
00:37:14,807 --> 00:37:17,844
Virgin! Virgin!

521
00:37:17,927 --> 00:37:20,521
[ Screaming ]

522
00:37:21,887 --> 00:37:23,957
- Friday!
- Let's move!

523
00:37:31,367 --> 00:37:33,278
Help!

524
00:37:33,367 --> 00:37:34,720
Can you swim?

525
00:37:34,807 --> 00:37:37,241
Red Cross. Junior Lifesaver
with clusters.

526
00:37:37,327 --> 00:37:39,238
Silly me.

527
00:37:45,087 --> 00:37:48,204
- Friday!
- Streebek?

528
00:37:48,287 --> 00:37:50,596
l found the snake.

529
00:37:50,687 --> 00:37:53,121
Help! Help!

530
00:37:54,167 --> 00:37:56,237
- Help!
- Hang in there. l'm coming.

531
00:37:56,327 --> 00:37:58,966
What goes on?
Who are those two clowns?

532
00:37:59,047 --> 00:38:01,356
Who are you?

533
00:38:01,447 --> 00:38:04,200
Friday, Streebek,
Los Angeles police officers.

534
00:38:08,287 --> 00:38:11,677
- Where are you from?
- Anaheim.

535
00:38:13,287 --> 00:38:15,357
Her favourite colour is blue.

536
00:38:15,447 --> 00:38:17,517
Jesus Christ! l'm about to be eaten!

537
00:38:19,847 --> 00:38:23,556
Some big guys grabbed me
off the street last night.

538
00:38:25,127 --> 00:38:30,201
- Were you sexually assaulted?
- No, thank God. They needed a virgin.

539
00:38:31,207 --> 00:38:33,516
You're still a virgin?

540
00:38:34,767 --> 00:38:37,361
My hat's off to you, ma'am.
Hope you stay that way.

541
00:38:37,447 --> 00:38:40,359
[ Cheering ]

542
00:38:40,447 --> 00:38:44,076
Streebek, quick! Do something.
