543
00:38:44,167 --> 00:38:46,806
Distract it.

544
00:39:11,687 --> 00:39:13,359
Anybody need boots?

545
00:39:17,087 --> 00:39:18,406
Stop them!

546
00:39:18,487 --> 00:39:19,840
Go!

547
00:39:33,607 --> 00:39:36,485
Kill the good! Kill the good!

548
00:39:36,567 --> 00:39:40,606
Kill the good! Kill the good!
Kill the good! Kill the good!

