950
01:09:33,247 --> 01:09:35,886
January 9, 8:37 a.m.

951
01:09:35,967 --> 01:09:38,561
My name's Streebek.
l'm a cop.

952
01:09:38,647 --> 01:09:40,000
l overslept.

953
01:09:42,167 --> 01:09:46,638
Curiously enough, l still hadn't heard
from my anal-retentive ex-partner...

954
01:09:46,727 --> 01:09:49,844
although l was sure he'd be proud to
know l was making a concerted effort...

955
01:09:49,927 --> 01:09:52,202
to personally develop
a close relationship...

956
01:09:52,287 --> 01:09:55,518
with one of my sisters
in the Los Angeles Police Department.

957
01:10:17,167 --> 01:10:19,727
l placed a call
to the virgin Connie Swail...

958
01:10:19,807 --> 01:10:22,844
but according to the girl's mother,
she hadn't come home either.

959
01:10:22,927 --> 01:10:25,646
l don't know what to say, Mrs. Swail.

960
01:10:25,727 --> 01:10:28,241
l'm beginning to be concerned myself.

961
01:10:28,327 --> 01:10:32,115
No, Joe Friday has never
stayed out all night, either.

962
01:10:32,207 --> 01:10:35,677
The day he was born,
his mother had him home by 9:00.

963
01:10:35,767 --> 01:10:39,680
Well, let's both stay in touch
in case we hear from them.

964
01:10:39,767 --> 01:10:41,723
Thank you, Mrs. Swail.

965
01:10:44,767 --> 01:10:47,565
Oh, my goodness.
l'm gonna be late for my stake-out.

966
01:10:48,687 --> 01:10:50,598
As enchanting as Robin was...

967
01:10:50,687 --> 01:10:54,521
l still couldn't get my mind off
what happened to Joe Friday.

968
01:10:54,607 --> 01:10:56,802
For one misguided moment...

969
01:10:56,887 --> 01:11:00,084
l actually pictured my ex-partner
introducing that little cupcake...

970
01:11:00,167 --> 01:11:04,001
to the one piece of equipment that
wasn't issued to him by the department.

971
01:11:04,087 --> 01:11:08,524
But then l realized Joe would never
spring for the price of a motel room.

972
01:11:08,607 --> 01:11:12,043
And since having sex in a Yugo
was a logistical impossibility...

973
01:11:12,127 --> 01:11:15,199
l came to the conclusion
that something must be wrong.

974
01:11:15,287 --> 01:11:16,879
Who cares?

975
01:11:16,967 --> 01:11:18,764
Listen to me, Captain.

976
01:11:18,847 --> 01:11:21,805
Joe Friday was the most dedicated cop
in this city.

977
01:11:21,887 --> 01:11:24,720
Okay, so maybe all his dogs
aren't attached to one leash.

978
01:11:24,807 --> 01:11:27,321
He's thickheaded, insensitive
and reactionary.

979
01:11:27,407 --> 01:11:30,797
And generally less fun to be around
than any person l've ever met.

980
01:11:30,887 --> 01:11:33,606
Still, he was my partner.

981
01:11:33,687 --> 01:11:36,042
You want to find Joe Friday?

982
01:11:36,127 --> 01:11:40,040
My advice is to start checking out
the sanitariums.

983
01:11:41,647 --> 01:11:43,478
- Hey, Pep.
- What's shaking?

984
01:11:43,567 --> 01:11:45,842
- Hey, you!
- Me, Pep?

985
01:11:46,887 --> 01:11:49,196
Detective Streebek to you.
Let's get this mop trimmed.

986
01:11:49,287 --> 01:11:51,278
Stop shaving with a pocketknife,
and next time you eat your lunch...

987
01:11:51,367 --> 01:11:53,198
put it in your stomach,
not on your uniform.

988
01:11:53,287 --> 01:11:56,006
You're a disgrace to this department
and that badge.

989
01:12:11,367 --> 01:12:13,278
You're late, Jerry.

990
01:12:14,887 --> 01:12:19,438
l saw your announcement about my
so-called million-dollar contribution.

991
01:12:19,527 --> 01:12:21,518
Do yourself a favour, friend.

992
01:12:22,767 --> 01:12:24,246
Try the lottery.

993
01:12:24,327 --> 01:12:26,204
The lottery l can fix.

994
01:12:26,287 --> 01:12:28,482
Our problem is Mayor Parvin.

995
01:12:28,567 --> 01:12:32,640
l'm afraid he is not
''going gentle into that good night.''

996
01:12:32,727 --> 01:12:34,080
Say what?

997
01:12:34,167 --> 01:12:38,046
That he is not responding
to our pressure to resign.

998
01:12:38,127 --> 01:12:40,687
We're gonna have to push him
over the edge.

999
01:12:40,767 --> 01:12:44,840
Your million-dollar contribution
will insure his presence at your party.

1000
01:12:44,927 --> 01:12:49,364
Just make sure he turns into
a drug-crazed idiot, with pictures.

1001
01:12:49,447 --> 01:12:52,086
Once he's politically dead,
Commissioner Kirkpatrick...

1002
01:12:52,167 --> 01:12:54,442
will be a shoo-in to replace him
in the next election.

1003
01:12:54,527 --> 01:12:57,837
You and l will split control
of the city.

1004
01:12:57,927 --> 01:12:59,997
You will monopolize all pornography.

1005
01:13:00,087 --> 01:13:03,602
Half the poor dumb sheep in Los Angeles
will be forking over money...

1006
01:13:03,687 --> 01:13:05,643
to buy your sleaze...

1007
01:13:05,727 --> 01:13:08,400
while the other half will be funding me
with the means to fight it.

1008
01:13:09,847 --> 01:13:11,200
Reverend...

1009
01:13:12,327 --> 01:13:14,795
you got balls as big as church bells.

1010
01:13:16,327 --> 01:13:17,806
Thank you.

1011
01:13:33,927 --> 01:13:37,522
Jonathan, l do not trust that man.

1012
01:13:37,607 --> 01:13:40,405
Thank goodness he trusts me.

1013
01:13:40,487 --> 01:13:42,682
That socially-retarded hedonist...

1014
01:13:42,767 --> 01:13:46,077
actually believes he's going
to be alive tomorrow.

1015
01:14:21,767 --> 01:14:23,359
Where's Joe Friday?

1016
01:14:36,447 --> 01:14:37,800
lt's no use.

1017
01:14:37,887 --> 01:14:39,718
These knots are too tight.

1018
01:14:39,807 --> 01:14:42,275
Untie the girl.
She's coming with me.

1019
01:14:44,807 --> 01:14:48,880
You hypocrite. lf you were decent,
you'd let her go and kill me instead.

1020
01:14:48,967 --> 01:14:50,320
lnstead?

1021
01:14:51,647 --> 01:14:56,516
But, my dear Sergeant Friday,
l'd always planned on killing you.

1022
01:14:56,607 --> 01:14:59,167
How do you see yourself
going down in history?

1023
01:14:59,247 --> 01:15:01,477
Pagan or reverend,
devil or angel?

1024
01:15:01,567 --> 01:15:04,764
Why, both, of course.

1025
01:15:04,847 --> 01:15:07,077
One can't exist without the other.

1026
01:15:07,167 --> 01:15:09,920
Without the Jerry Caesars,
there'd be no moral outrage.

1027
01:15:10,007 --> 01:15:12,077
What's the good of moral outrage...

1028
01:15:12,167 --> 01:15:15,239
unless you have something tangible
to direct it against?

1029
01:15:15,327 --> 01:15:17,887
By this time tomorrow,
thanks to that poison gas...

1030
01:15:17,967 --> 01:15:20,561
you've been tracking
like some flu-ridden bloodhound...

1031
01:15:20,647 --> 01:15:24,401
Mr Caesar will be sitting
in that big Jacuzzi in the sky...

1032
01:15:24,487 --> 01:15:26,796
and l'll control both sides
of the equation.

1033
01:15:26,887 --> 01:15:30,163
Sure, but like every other psycho
in this city with a foolproof plan...

1034
01:15:30,247 --> 01:15:33,000
you've forgotten you're facing the
finest fighting force ever assembled.

1035
01:15:34,407 --> 01:15:35,760
The lsraelis?

1036
01:15:35,847 --> 01:15:38,486
Try the decent, hardworking
men and women of Los Angeles.

1037
01:15:40,487 --> 01:15:42,682
Forgotten about them?

1038
01:15:42,767 --> 01:15:44,883
My dear Sergeant...

1039
01:15:44,967 --> 01:15:48,277
l'm absolutely counting on them.

1040
01:15:50,607 --> 01:15:52,484
- Joe.
- [ Whirley Laughs ]

1041
01:15:52,567 --> 01:15:54,637
Joe?

1042
01:16:28,167 --> 01:16:32,319
