You may have taken a wrong turn,
but there's time to straighten out.

1043
01:16:32,407 --> 01:16:34,602
You're the one that's gonna
straighten out, cop...

1044
01:16:34,687 --> 01:16:36,518
all the way down the mountain.

1045
01:16:40,767 --> 01:16:42,120
Let's go, Streebek.

1046
