1126
01:23:59,487 --> 01:24:01,921
l'll be joining a special passenger...

1127
01:24:02,007 --> 01:24:05,522
aboard my jet for a few
restful days in Acapulco.

1128
01:24:05,607 --> 01:24:08,041
Don't forget to leave a Pagan card...

1129
01:24:08,127 --> 01:24:10,277
so the police and Mr Caesar's
next of kin...

1130
01:24:10,367 --> 01:24:14,121
will give us proper credit
for returning his magazines.

1131
01:24:14,207 --> 01:24:16,801
Oh, and, Emil...

1132
01:24:16,887 --> 01:24:18,798
ever forward.

1133
01:24:46,167 --> 01:24:48,840
Police officers! Clear the road.

1134
01:24:56,967 --> 01:24:58,719
''Police officers.

