- Move it!
- Go! Go! Go! Go!

1137
01:25:31,887 --> 01:25:36,722
What the-- Cops! Break out the weapons!
Break out the masks!

1138
01:26:16,167 --> 01:26:17,998
We're pinned down.
Hold your positions!

1139
01:26:32,007 --> 01:26:34,396
All right, boys, let's do it!

1140
01:27:22,847 --> 01:27:24,724
Thank God, it's Friday!

1141
