01:28:01,127 --> 01:28:02,321
Thanks, partner.

1147
01:28:02,407 --> 01:28:05,843
Read him his rights, Pep.

1148
01:28:05,927 --> 01:28:07,280
''Pep''?

1149
01:28:08,527 --> 01:28:10,483
